data.description: Luxurious waterfront living awaits you. This newly renovated home sits-on 7 acres of land with 254 feet of water frontage, providing plenty of space for outdoor activities. With 3 Bedrooms, 4.5 bath, and 4,200 sqft. of living space this home offers ample space and comfort. New modern style kitchen, quartz countertops, and SS appliances. Each spacious bedroom has its own bathroom. The primary bedroom is a true oasis, complete with his & hers bathroom, walk-in closets, and access to a private outdoor deck. Large 26 x 18 game room with outdoor access. The outdoor entertaining area includes a heated saltwater pool with spa, screened-in entertainment area, boat dock with 2 hoist, and fishing pier. The fishing pier and boat dock provide easy access to water for boating and fishing enthusiasts. This home also includes a 40x 60 metal workshop offering endless possibilities for hobbies, storage, or even a home business. Security system throughout equipped with monitors. Property comes equipped with a 75KW Cummins Diesel Generator, built-in 250 gallon diesel tank and hilt, generator can power entire property including pool and building. HVAC and tankless hot water heater replaced 2021, roof replaced in 2020. Lot 3-F-2 is included in sale.  Home is on the list to be raised. Flood Insurance Premium $806.
